    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant attention to be roadworthy. The engine currently runs roughly and there are noticeable leaks that need immediate repair, along with a suspension that feels quite worn. Visually, the car has substantial body rust, fading paint, and several large dents, while the interior shows heavy wear, including torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. It is best suited as a project car for an enthusiast or for someone looking for a source of spare parts.",
      "price": 6500.0,
