      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle remains in impeccable showroom condition, exhibiting no discernible wear and maintaining its original factory luster. Every component has been meticulously scrutinized to ensure it meets the most exacting standards of excellence. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle that transcends the standard pre-owned experience, offering uncompromising quality for the sophisticated driver.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
